column1: # Annual estimates of Tatchun Chinook at WEIR
# Overview of site and current methods at https://www.yukonriverpanel.com/re-fund-project/tatchun-creek-chinook-enumeration/adfg=sonar.site_info&site=16
# Estimate = run size of XYZ Chinook at in the ?Tatchun River?
# SE = Standard Error calculated based on INSERT
# p10 and p90 = 10th abd 90th percentiles of the ?posterior distribution?
# CV = Coefficient of Variation = SE / Estimate

column10: weir was removed early (August 24) due to flooding
